the Empire State Building.

76
00:14:07,552 --> 00:14:11,010
I think I’ll call it The Skyscraper Gaper Caper.

77
00:14:11,089 --> 00:14:13,455
Sounds really exciting, sir.

78
00:14:14,526 --> 00:14:17,154
