being your lawyer.

122
00:16:58,523 --> 00:17:01,754
You know, knowing how the strip
was coming out and all.

123
00:17:02,427 --> 00:17:05,487
For a moment there, they were actually...

124
00:17:08,199 --> 00:17:10,030
...kinda proud of their old man.

125
